<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="imageSection position-relative">
            <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/aboutus2.jpg" alt="Event Planning Carousel Image 1" height="450px">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/aboutus.jpg" alt="Event Planning Carousel Image 2" height="450px">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/images/aboutus3.jpg" alt="Event Planning Carousel Image 3" height="450px">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-bs-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-bs-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="overlayText">Our mission: streamline event planning with intuitive, flawless tools</div>
        </div>
        <div class="contentSection mt-4">
            <header id="aboutUsHeading" class="mb-3">About us</header>
            <p id="paragraphAboutUs">
                At Event Planner, we simplify event planning with innovative, user-friendly tools designed to
                streamline every step of the process. Our platform helps you effortlessly manage logistics,
                coordinate with teams, and ensure a flawless execution of your events. With a focus on efficiency
                and ease, we are dedicated to transforming complex planning into a seamless experience. Trust us to
                bring your vision to life and make your events memorable.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flip">Welcome to Our Company</div>
        <div class="panel">
            At Hexa, we empower you to take charge of your own events with confidence and ease.
            Whether it’s a wedding, a corporate meeting, or a personal celebration, we provide the tools, resources, and
            expertise you need to make your event a success.
        </div>
        <div class="flip">Our Story</div>
        <div class="panel">
            Founded in 2018 by Alex Rivera, Hexa emerged from a desire to make event planning
            accessible and manageable for everyone. After years of working in the event planning industry,
            Alex recognized the need for a platform that supports individuals and organizations in
            planning their own events without the need for a full-service planner.
        </div>
        <div class="flip">Our Approach</div>
        <div class="panel">
            We believe that successful events start with a solid plan. Our approach focuses on providing
            you with comprehensive resources, including planning guides, checklists, and templates. We also offer expert
            advice and support to help you make
            informed decisions and manage the event planning process smoothly.
        </div>
        <header id="ourTeamHeading" class="mt-4 mb-3">Our Team</header>
        <div class="gallery-container">
            <div class="gallery">
                <a target="_blank" href="~/images/team1.jpg">
                    <img src="~/images/team1.jpg" alt="Jennifer" width="600" height="400">
                </a>
                <div class="desc">Jennifer</div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery">
                <a target="_blank" href="~/images/team2.jpg">
                    <img src="~/images/team2.jpg" alt="Aliyah" width="600" height="400">
                </a>
                <div class="desc">Aliyah</div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery">
                <a target="_blank" href="~/images/team3.jpg">
                    <img src="~/images/team3.jpg" alt="Inika" width="600" height="400">
                </a>
                <div class="desc"><p>Inika</p><p>Team Leader</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery">
                <a target="_blank" href="~/images/team2.jpg">
                    <img src="~/images/team2.jpg" alt="Namya" width="600" height="400">
                </a>
                <div class="desc">Namya</div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery">
                <a target="_blank" href="~/images/team1.jpg">
                    <img src="~/images/team1.jpg" alt="Viti" width="600" height="400">
                </a>
                <div class="desc">Viti</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
